Package: waveleT
Type: Package
Title: Use wavelet transforms to describe a signal (time series or spatial series) at multiple scales.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Lise", "Vaudor",
      email = "lise.vaudor@ens-lyon.fr",
